英國馬致勝一擊是2021年加冕盃冠軍<ref>{{Cite news|first=Peter|last=Scargill|url=https://www.racingpost.com/news/race-reports/william-muir-and-chris-grassick-enjoy-group-1-glory-as-pyledriver-denies-al-aasy/493390|title='Racing is a wonderful sport' - emotional Dwyer claims Group 1 on Pyledriver|publisher=Racing Post|date=2021-06-04|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125142528/https://www.racingpost.com/news/race-reports/william-muir-and-chris-grassick-enjoy-group-1-glory-as-pyledriver-denies-al-aasy/493390|dead-url=no}}</ref>，因傷久休復出後，輕取一場膠沙地表列賽邱吉爾園錦標<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://www.attheraces.com/news/2021/November/13/coronation-cup-hero-pyledriver-delights-on-lingfield-return|title=Coronation Cup hero Pyledriver delights on Lingfield return|publisher=[[天空體育|天空體育]]|date=2021-11-13|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125142852/https://www.attheraces.com/news/2021/November/13/coronation-cup-hero-pyledriver-delights-on-lingfield-return|dead-url=no}}</ref>。耀滿瓶是2019年香港瓶得主，雖然此後沒贏過頭馬，但是今年征戰女皇盃跑獲亞軍，今場賽事並配上2019年贏馬組合莫雷拉<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://p.nikkansports.com/goku-uma/news/article.zpl?topic_id=1&id=202111050001059&year=2021&month=11&day=5|title=グローリーヴェイズはモレイラ騎手で香港ヴァーズへ|publisher=[[日刊體育|日刊體育]]|date=2021-11-05|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125142620/https://p.nikkansports.com/goku-uma/news/article.zpl?topic_id=1&id=202111050001059&year=2021&month=11&day=5|dead-url=no}}</ref>。時時有餘是2020年香港瓶季軍<ref name="hkvase 2020" />，最近於遮打盃跑獲亞軍。愚者眼界今年保持定，並克服心律不正問題，札幌紀念賽後一個多月可以恢復比賽<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://news.netkeiba.com/?pid=news_view&no=193576|title=【次走】ステイフーリッシュは京都大賞典へ/馬三郎のつぶやき|publisher=Daily Sports|date=2021-09-30|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125144228/https://news.netkeiba.com/?pid=news_view&no=193576|dead-url=no}}</ref>。業界巨頭曾贏出2020年香港瓶<ref name="hkvase 2020">{{Cite news|first=Leo|last=Schlink|url=https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2020/12/13/%e8%8e%ab%e9%9b%85%e8%88%87%e5%b2%b3%e4%bc%af%e4%bb%81%e6%86%91%e6%a5%ad%e7%95%8c%e5%b7%a8%e9%a0%ad%e6%94%bb%e4%b8%8b%e6%b5%aa%e7%90%b4%e8%a1%a8%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%93%b6/|title=莫雅與岳伯仁憑「業界巨頭」攻下浪琴表香港瓶|publisher=香港賽馬會|date=2020-12-13|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125143336/https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2020/12/13/%e8%8e%ab%e9%9b%85%e8%88%87%e5%b2%b3%e4%bc%af%e4%bb%81%e6%86%91%e6%a5%ad%e7%95%8c%e5%b7%a8%e9%a0%ad%e6%94%bb%e4%b8%8b%e6%b5%aa%e7%90%b4%e8%a1%a8%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%93%b6/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。精神威以慢放方式贏出2021年馬會盃，羅富全賽後亦決定讓馬匹參加香港瓶<ref>{{Cite news|first=Leo|last=Schlink|url=https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2021/11/21/%e7%b2%be%e7%a5%9e%e5%a8%81%e7%9b%b4%e9%a0%98%e5%88%b0%e5%ba%95%e6%8f%9a%e5%a8%81%e4%b8%ad%e9%8a%80%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e9%a6%ac%e6%9c%83%e7%9b%83/?b_cid=EWRNRNC|title=「精神威」直領到底揚威中銀香港馬會盃|publisher=香港賽馬會|date=2021-11-21|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125145832/https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2021/11/21/%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E5%A8%81%E7%9B%B4%E9%A0%98%E5%88%B0%E5%BA%95%E6%8F%9A%E5%A8%81%E4%B8%AD%E9%8A%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E7%9B%83/?b_cid=EWRNRNC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。勇猛神駒是2021年皇太后紀念盃冠軍<ref>{{Cite news|first=Leo|last=Schlink|url=https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2021/05/02/%e5%8b%87%e7%8c%9b%e7%a5%9e%e9%a7%92%e6%94%bb%e4%b8%8b%e7%9a%87%e5%a4%aa%e5%90%8e%e7%b4%80%e5%bf%b5%e7%9b%83/?b_cid=EWRNRNCC|title=「勇猛神駒」攻下皇太后紀念盃|publisher=香港賽馬會|date=2021-05-02|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125145909/https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2021/05/02/%E5%8B%87%E7%8C%9B%E7%A5%9E%E9%A7%92%E6%94%BB%E4%B8%8B%E7%9A%87%E5%A4%AA%E5%90%8E%E7%B4%80%E5%BF%B5%E7%9B%83/?b_cid=EWRNRNCC|dead-url=no}}</ref>。倚蓬萊贏出多場法國雌馬分級賽，是兩項二級賽及三級賽得主，全為雌馬賽，聖格盧大賽跑獲亞軍。這也是法國練馬師羅