nt |publisher= [[南華早報|南華早報]] |date= 2021-05-23 |accessdate= 2021-12-09 |archive-date= 2021-12-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211209042604/https://www.scmp.com/sport/racing/article/3134552/future-looking-bright-john-size-puts-courier-wonder-path-hong-kong |dead-url= no }}</ref>。拉丁城市曾於兩歲時贏出阪神兩歲牝馬錦標<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://p.nikkansports.com/goku-uma/news/article.zpl?topic_id=1&id=201912080000629&year=2019&month=12&day=9|title=怪物娘レシステンシア圧勝、来春の主役に／阪神ＪＦ|publisher=日刊體育|date=2019-12-09|accessdate=2021-11-26|archive-date=2021-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126080935/https://p.nikkansports.com/goku-uma/news/article.zpl?topic_id=1&id=201912080000629&year=2019&month=12&day=9|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2021年轉戰短途賽，除了在[[高松宮紀念賽|高松宮紀念賽]]及[[短途馬錦標|短途馬錦標]]跑入亞席代表作是贏出二級賽人馬錦標<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://hochi.news/articles/20210912-OHT1T51151.html?page=1|title=【セントウルＳ】レシステンシアＶ　Ｇ前ヒヤリも「ひと伸びした」ルメール騎手は評価|publisher=[[體育報知|體育報知]]|date=2021-09-12|accessdate=2021-11-25|archive-date=2021-11-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211125145522/https://hochi.news/articles/20210912-OHT1T51151.html?page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

