香港短途錦標發生了嚴重連環墮馬意外，轉彎時君達星失蹄倒地，令騎師希威森墮馬<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://www.sportingpost.co.za/2021/12/lyle-latest-on-the-champion/|title=Lyle – Latest On The Champion|publisher=Sporting Post|date=2021-12-13|accessdate=2021-12-13|archive-date=2021-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211213155527/https://www.sportingpost.co.za/2021/12/lyle-latest-on-the-champion/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，繼而累及後方的肥仔叻叻、錶之未來和日本外隊馬妙發靈機相撞，令騎師田泰安、福永祐一<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://hochi.news/articles/20211213-OHT1T51133.html?page=1|title=左鎖骨骨折の福永祐一騎手に帰国の許可　妻・松尾翠アナがインスタグラムで明かす|publisher=[[體育報知|體育報知]]|date=2021-12-13|accessdate=2021-12-13|archive-date=2021-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211213155523/https://hochi.news/articles/20211213-OHT1T51133.html?page=1|dead-url=no}}</ref>和潘頓<ref>{{Cite news |first=Nick |last=Hluchaniuk 9 hours ago |url=https://www.punters.com.au/news/zac-purton-in-good-spirits-after-fall-20221213/ |title=Zac Purton in good spirits as he recovers from injuries sustained in Hong Kong fall |publisher=punters.com.au |date=2021-12-13 |accessdate=2021-12-13 |archive-date=2021-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211213155519/https://www.punters.com.au/news/zac-purton-in-good-spirits-after-fall-20221213/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>墮馬，至於後方的野田重擊也因勒避而失位。最為不幸的是，君達星以及肥仔叻叻因傷勢太重而遭人道毀滅<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/711508/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4%E5%A2%AE%E9%A6%AC%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E5%85%A9%E9%A6%AC%E9%A0%88%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%AF%80%E6%BB%85-%E5%90%9B%E9%81%94%E6%98%9F%E6%9B%BE%E5%85%A9%E8%A9%95-%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97 |title=香港01：沙田馬場墮馬意外兩馬須人道毀滅　君達星曾兩評「表現難以接受」 |access-date=2022-01-18 |archive-date=2022-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107154015/https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/711508/%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4%E5%A2%AE%E9%A6%AC%E6%84%8F%E5%A4%96%E5%85%A9%E9%A6%AC%E9%A0%88%E4%BA%BA%E9%81%93%E6%AF%80%E6%BB%85-%E5%90%9B%E9%81%94%E6%98%9F%E6%9B%BE%E5%85%A9%E8%A9%95-%E8%A1%A8%E7%8F%BE%E9%9B%A3%E4%BB%A5%E6%8E%A5%E5%8F%97 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。因應墮馬事件，香港賽馬會決定該場賽事及餘下兩場國際賽頒獎儀式從簡，取消國歌演奏<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2021/12/12/%e6%9c%ac%e6%9c%83%e8%81%b2%e6%98%8e/|title=本會聲明|publisher=香港賽馬會|date=2021-12-12|accessdate=2021-12-13|archive-date=2021-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211213085902/https://racingnews.hkjc.com/chinese/2021/12/12/%E6%9C%AC%E6%9C%83%E8%81%B2%E6%98%8E/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://hd.stheadline.com/racing/racing_content.asp?contid=22018&srctype=r|title=馬會應變 值得一讚|publisher=[[頭條日報|頭條日報]]|date=2021-12-13|accessdate=2022-01-03|archive-date=2022-01-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220103142824/https://hd.stheadline.com/racing/racing_content.asp?contid=22018&srctype=r|dead-url=no}}</ref>。至於另外兩匹同樣被意外影響致其騎師墮馬的馬匹錶之未來和妙發靈機，前者錶之未來於檢查後沒有任何傷勢或異常情況，而後者妙發靈機初時外表沒有任何傷痕，但詳細檢查後發現左前膝腫脹及骨折，氣管多血<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://news.sp.netkeiba.com/?pid=news_view&no=197261|title=福永は左鎖骨骨折、ピクシーナイトも左前脚骨折|publisher=netkeiba|date=2021-12-12|accessdate=2021-12-12|archive-date=2021-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214163457/https://news.sp.netkeiba.com/?pid=news_view&no=197261|dead-url=no}}</ref>，幸好相關傷患不至於嚴重到馬匹需要人道毀滅，可以緩慢休養康復，而日媒報道其左前膝骨折，胸部肌肉受傷，需要相當時間治理<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/711838/%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%B3%BD-%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%A2%AE%E9%A6%AC-%E4%B8%89%E9%A8%8E%E5%B8%AB%E6%84%8F%E8%AD%98%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92%E5%90%84%E8%87%AA%E5%A0%B1%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89|title=賽馬．香港國際賽｜近年最嚴重墮馬　三騎師意識清醒各自報平安|publisher=香港01|date=2021-12-13|accessdate=2021-12-13|archive-date=2021-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211215134034/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E9%AB%94%E8%82%B2/711838/%E8%B3%BD%E9%A6%AC-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%B3%BD-%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B4%E6%9C%80%E5%9A%B4%E9%87%8D%E5%A2%AE%E9%A6%AC-%E4%B8%89%E9%A8%8E%E5%B8%AB%E6%84%8F%E8%AD%98%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92%E5%90%84%E8%87%AA%E5%A0%B1%E5%B9%B3%E5%AE%89|dead-url=no}}</ref>。繼2013年的香港短途錦標的騎師翟利隆策騎「捷威來」墮馬，因馬匹傷勢人道毀滅，騎師翟利隆被送往醫院。

