-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126144654/https://hochi.news/articles/20211123-OHT1T51158.html?page=1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。陳年美酒2020年攻下富士錦標，2021年[[杜拜草地大賽|杜拜草地大賽]]僅不敵{{link-en|諾斯勳爵 (馬)|Lord North (horse)|諾斯勳爵}}跑獲亞軍<ref>{{Cite news|first= Stuart|last= Riley|url= https://www.racingpost.com/news/international/in-for-a-big-year-lord-north-demolishes-dubai-turf-opposition-under-dettori/481148|title= In for a big year? Lord North demolishes Meydan opposition under Dettori|publisher= Racing Post|date= 2021-03-27|accessdate= 2021-11-26|archive-date= 2021-11-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211126083658/https://www.racingpost.com/news/international/in-for-a-big-year-lord-north-demolishes-dubai-turf-opposition-under-dettori/481148|dead-url= no}}</ref>。達心星是2021年香港打吡大賽冠軍<ref>{{Cite news|first=|last=|url=https://std.stheadline.com/racing/article/2343471/%E9%A6%AC%E7%B6%93-%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4%E6%B5%AE%E4%B8%96%E7%B9%AA-%E9%81%94%E5%BF%83%E6%98%9F%E5%8B%87%E5%A5%AA%E6%89%93%E5%90%A1|title=達心星勇奪打吡|publisher=[[星島日報|星島日報]]|date=2021-03-22|accessdate=2021-11-26|archive-date=2021-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211126082803/https://std.stheadline.com/racing/article/2343471/%E9%A6%AC%E7%B6%93-%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4%E6%B5%AE%E4%B8%96%E7%B9%AA-%E9%81%94%E5%BF%83%E6%98%9F%E5%8B%87%E5%A5%AA%E6%89%93%E5%90%A1|dead-url=no}}</ref>。勁搏是2021年香港經典一哩賽冠軍。幸運快車從一班賽重新上位，贏出[[樂聲盃|樂聲盃]]<ref>{{Cite news|first=Tom|last=Biddington|url=https://www.scmp.com/sport/racing/article/3155962/lucky-express-makes-play-hkir-issue-hinders-fantastic-treasure|title=Lucky Express makes play for HKIR as issue hinders Fantastic Treasure|publisher=[[南華早報|南華早報]]|date=2021-11-13|accessdate=2021-11-26|archive-date=2021-12-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211214163434/https://www.scmp.com/sport/racing/article/3155962/lucky-express-makes-play-hkir-issue-hinders-fantastic-treasure|dead-url=no}}</ref>。后土是2021年英國[[一千堅尼錦標|一千堅尼錦標]]冠軍<ref>{{Cite news|first= Lewis|last= Porteous|url= https://www.racingpost.com/news/race-reports/frankie-dettori-and-aidan-obrien-combine-for-classic-glory-with-mother-earth/487792|title= Mother of God! Frankie Dettori lands 1,000 Guineas on O'Brien's Mother Earth|publisher= Racing Post|date= 2021-05-02|accessdate= 2021-11-26|archive-date= 2021-11-26|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20211126081311/https://www.racingpost.com/news/race-reports/frankie-dettori-and-aidan-obrien-combine-for-classic-glory-with-mother-earth/487792|dead-url= no}}</ref>，亦贏出羅斯齊爾德大賽等。

